The evidence with the title 'The only 5 countries that meet NATO's defense spending ... ' says Feb 24, 2017  ... Just 5 of the 28 alliance members meet the requirement agreed upon in 2006 that members spend at least 2 percent of their gdp on defense .  ... More than the entire national economic output of all but 20 countries in the world .  ... Trump is not wrong when he says the U.S. pays more than its fair share . 
